title: Lyrics Born - Funky Hit Records - NEW MUSIC!
description:
Lyrics Born's forthcoming new album is titled 'AS U WERE'.  
The first song from that album is called "Funky Hit Records" featuring production by Lyrics Born and Trackademicks.

Lyrics Born is a Bay Area, CA MC who is one of the founders of Quannum Projects (DJ Shadow, Blackalicious, Latyrx) and one-half of the supergroup Latyrx with Lateef the Truthspeaker.

The song is a modern twist on old school 80's hip-hop and rap.
